      <div id="main" class="grid_12">
        <h1 class="title" id="page-title">Accommodation</h1>                                <div id="content-output"> 
          <div id="node-32" class="node post clear-block">



  <div class="meta post-info">
  
    </div>

  <div class="content">
    <p>FSCONS does not provide accommodation, but we know several great places which do, depending on your budget!<br />
You can also find some additional information about sleeping in Gothenburg at <a href="http://wikitravel.org/en/G%C3%B6teborg#Sleep">Wikitravel Göteborg: Sleeping</a>.</p>
<h2>Hostels</h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.hostel-gothenburg.com/"><strong>Hostelling International Stigbergsliden</strong></a> Our recommendation. Please mention codename <em>"FSCONS"</em> when booking for a special price.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.sgsveckobostader.se/item.aspx?id=448">SGS Veckobostäder</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.slottsskogenvh.se/english/index.htm">Slottsskogens Youth Hostel</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.goteborgsvandrarhem.se/en">Göteborgs Vandrarhem</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.grethes.com/eg.htm">Grethe's Hostel</a></li>
</ul>
<h2>Couch-Surfing</h2>
<p>We have set up both a <a href="http://www.couchsurfing.org/group.html?gid=22506">group</a>, and an <a href="http://www.couchsurfing.org/meetings.html?mid=44842">event</a>, to help couch-surfers get in touch for FSCONS. <a href="http://www.couchsurfing.org/help.html">What's this?</a></p>
<h2>Hotels</h2>
<p>If you're looking to book a hotel room, you can use the following form to find a hotel that is suitable.</p>
<p><iframe frameborder="0" scrolling="no" width="100%" height="400" src="http://book.hotelzon.com/portallogin?loginname=FFKP&amp;password=portal&amp;domain=hzs" /></iframe></p>
  </div>

  </div>        </div><!-- /#content-output -->
